</head>
<body>
  <main>
    <h1>Mobile Web Console Hub</h1>
    <p>This instance provides browser-based Linux workspaces that are created and managed through the admin interface. Users can receive either terminal workspaces or full Linux desktops over WebVNC, with separate network policies per environment.</p>
    <p>Use the admin panel to create users, generate their containers, and distribute the resulting workspace URLs.</p>
